data.meta_description: pagalguy - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document summarizes important current affairs news from June 2016 that would be relevant for banking, SSC, insurance and UPSC exams. It discusses several topics including the Reserve Bank of India maintaining the status quo on policy rates in its monetary policy review while introducing a new scheme for restructuring stressed assets. It also summarizes other recent news in financial and banking sectors such as changes to tax deductions on PF withdrawals, approval of an India Post Payments Bank, and updates on actions from other banks.
